<normalizedToken originalValue="São">Sao</normalizedToken>
Miguel (intertidal zone down to 20 m depth: DBUA 176, 1 spm; DBUA 637, 1 spm; DBUA 683, 1 spm; DBUA 700, 2 spm; DBUA 708/F, 1 spm; DBUA 719, 1 valve; DBUA 721, 1 spm; DBUA 730, 3 spm; DBUA 731, 1 spm; DBUA 732, 2 spm; DBUA 733, 1 spm; DBUA 748, 2 spm; DBUA 751, 1 spm; DBUA 752, 2 spm; DBUA 767, 1 spm; DBUA 794, 2 spm; DBUA 1056, 3 spm).
</paragraph>
